---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
    title="About Me"
    description="Cybersecurity Professional | Threat Intelligence | Network Security"
    pubDate={new Date('April 1, 2025')}
>
    <section>
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>
            I am a <strong>GIAC-certified Cybersecurity professional</strong> with hands-on experience in advanced cybersecurity tools and technologies, including 
            <strong>Nmap, Wireshark, Metasploit, and tcpdump</strong>. I specialize in:
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>Threat Intelligence & Incident Response</li>
            <li>Vulnerability Assessment & Network Security</li>
            <li>Cyber Risk Management & Compliance</li>
            <li>Cloud & Container Security</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
            I excel in translating complex technical concepts into clear, actionable insights for non-technical audiences, 
            and I am committed to continuous learning in the ever-evolving cybersecurity landscape.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Certifications</h2>
        <div class="certifications">
            <div class="cert">
                <svg width="100" height="100" viewBox="0 0 100 100">
                    <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="48" stroke="gold" stroke-width="4" fill="black" />
                    <text x="50%" y="50%" fill="white" font-size="14px" font-weight="bold" text-anchor="middle" dy=".3em">GCIH</text>
                </svg>
                <p>GCIH - Incident Handler</p>
            </div>
            <div class="cert">
                <svg width="100" height="100" viewBox="0 0 100 100">
                    <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="48" stroke="silver" stroke-width="4" fill="black" />
                    <text x="50%" y="50%" fill="white" font-size="14px" font-weight="bold" text-anchor="middle" dy=".3em">GSEC</text>
                </svg>
                <p>GSEC - Security Essentials</p>
            </div>
            <div class="cert">
                <svg width="100" height="100" viewBox="0 0 100 100">
                    <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="48" stroke="blue" stroke-width="4" fill="black" />
                    <text x="50%" y="50%" fill="white" font-size="14px" font-weight="bold" text-anchor="middle" dy=".3em">GCLD</text>
                </svg>
                <p>GCLD - Cloud Security</p>
            </div>
            <div class="cert">
                <svg width="100" height="100" viewBox="0 0 100 100">
                    <rect x="10" y="10" width="80" height="80" fill="#ff9900" />
                    <text x="50%" y="50%" fill="black" font-size="12px" font-weight="bold" text-anchor="middle" dy=".3em">AWS</text>
                </svg>
                <p>AWS Cloud Practitioner</p>
            </div>
            <div class="cert">
                <svg width="100" height="100" viewBox="0 0 100 100">
                    <polygon points="50,10 90,90 10,90" fill="#0089d6" />
                    <text x="50%" y="60%" fill="white" font-size="12px" font-weight="bold" text-anchor="middle">Azure</text>
                </svg>
                <p>Azure Fundamentals</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>My Cybersecurity Journey</h2>
        <p>
            Over the years, I have participated in various cybersecurity competitions and projects, including:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>National Cyber League (NCL)</strong> - Ranked in the top 25%</li>
            <li><strong>SANS Internet Storm Center Internship</strong> - Threat Intelligence & Research</li>
            <li><strong>Homelab Projects</strong> - Setting up honeypots & analyzing attack vectors</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

</Layout>

<style>
.certifications {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 10px;
}
.cert {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 150px;
}
.cert svg {
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto;
}
</style>
